ave a new guest language this week, &lt;a href=&#34;https://codeberg.org/mauke/ploki&#34;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ploki&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, thanks to &lt;code&gt;mauke&lt;/code&gt;. We even have first contribution in &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/manwar/perlweeklychallenge-club/tree/master/challenge-378/mauke/ploki&#34;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ploki&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; by him.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
